My project will be a basketball pickup site where users can create and join games located around their area.

mvp: 
mvp will utilize geo locator. 
user will be able to login and create a basketball game. 
users will be able to join/check-in to created games. 
users can see how many players are checked into each game.
users can see what gym/location the games at.
users can see how many are checked into a game

DataBase: 
*stores all user accounts 
*stores created games 
stores users past games

views/pages: 
log in modal
signup page 
profile dashboard 
NBA news page 
search for games page


